title: ETH v1 Listing: Add YGG market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list YGG on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market with a Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap — contingent on decentralized oracle coverage.

Proposal: Forum 
https://forum.cream.finance/t/new-asset-proposal-ygg-yield-guild-games/1922

Rational: Initiate GameFi coverage on C.R.E.A.M. markets.
We are voting pre-oracle coverage, so we are able to launch an YGG market day 1 of oracle launch.

For:
Add YGG market with Collateral Factor: 45% and Collateral Cap: $1M

Against:
Do not make any changes to ETH v1 market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
